      <body>
        <div xml:id="song45">
          <head rend="italic">A Smile, or Frown.</head>
          <head type="voice" rend="italic">For one, two or three voyces.</head>
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
        <div type="underlay">
            <lg type="stanza">
            <l>Though my torment far exceeds</l>
            <l>his whole hart the Vulture feeds,</l>
            <l>and my endless pains excell</l>
            <l>his that rowls the stone in Hell;</l>
            <l>If my <hi rend="italic">Julia</hi> do but smile,</l>
            <l>I can laugh and sing the while.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
        <div>
           <lg type="stanza">
             <l>Though my Fortunes greater were</l>
             <l>Then the <hi rend="italic">Macedonians</hi> Heire:</l>
             <l>Could I boast of greater glory</l>
             <l>Then the <hi rend="italic">Scithians</hi> Shepheards story?</l>
             <l>If my <hi rend="italic">Julia</hi> do but frown,</l>
             <l>All my Pompe were overthrown.</l>
           </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
